WEBVTT

00:02.759 --> 00:07.875
In China, President Xi Jinping and US Secretary of State John Kerry...

00:08.429 --> 00:11.902
...meet and reaffirm their commitment to ensure North Korea...

00:12.002 --> 00:14.035
...ends its nuclear weapons program.

00:14.977 --> 00:19.991
Fresh clashes between troops and outlawed PKK militants in Turkey's southeast...

00:20.373 --> 00:21.793
...claim 23 lives.

00:23.713 --> 00:28.513
The United Nations General Assembly holds a minute of silence to honor the victims...

00:28.589 --> 00:32.697
...of the Holocaust during International Holocaust Remembrance Day.

00:36.003 --> 00:39.477
Hundreds of Iraqi asylum seekers are returning home,...

00:39.959 --> 00:42.855
...frustrated by the slow asylum process in Germany.

00:45.183 --> 00:49.079
And finally from Kenya, the presidents of Nigeria and Somalia...

00:49.172 --> 00:52.437
...join their Kenyan counterpart in a memorial ceremony...

00:52.521 --> 00:55.397
...for soldiers killed by al-Shabab Islamists.

